channel.title: Comments on: Is My Mic Working Now?

item.title: By: Mihneth
item.dc:creator: Mihneth
item.description: I like vice chats utility. I just hate wearing headphones. It kind of defeats the purpose of a snazzy 7.1 setup when you have to don the headphones to talk to people.

item.title: By: Byron Ellacott
item.dc:creator: Byron Ellacott
item.description: Check out zebhosting for your vent server. They've been charging me $15/mo for a 70-person TS server, I believe TS and Vent cost the same amount. Seems like a decent price. I'd give a full URL but you might think I'm a spam bot.
